// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-2855 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 45233c44-7621-5467-97a5-095f169464d9

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
